For the Ghislaine Maxwell case, I'd like to request approval to travel with our case agents to Durango, Colorado next week

and return on Thursday (4/15). Other than flights and a hotel, I don't anticipate any other travel expenses for the trip. 
Thanks very much, and hope you're doing well--
